graph TB
    subgraph OGXOperator["OGX K8s Operator"]
        direction TB
        Reconciler["OGXServerReconciler<br/>(Controller)"]
        Webhook["OGXServerValidator<br/>(Validating Webhook)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
        KustomizePipeline["Kustomize Pipeline<br/>(Manifest Renderer)"]
        LegacyAdoption["Legacy Adoption<br/>(Migration Controller)"]

        Reconciler -->|renders manifests via| KustomizePipeline
        Reconciler -->|triggers| LegacyAdoption
    end

    User["Data Scientist / Platform Admin"] -->|creates/updates| OGXServerCR["OGXServer CR<br/>(ogx.io/v1beta1)"]
    OGXServerCR -->|validated by| Webhook
    OGXServerCR -->|watched by| Reconciler

    LegacyLLSD["LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>(llamastack.io/v1alpha1)<br/>deprecated"] -.->|adopted by| LegacyAdoption

    subgraph ManagedResources["Managed Kubernetes Resources"]
        direction LR
        Deployment["Deployment"]
        Service["Service<br/>8321/TCP"]
        SA["ServiceAccount"]
        PVC["PersistentVolumeClaim"]
        NP["NetworkPolicy"]
        Ingress["Ingress<br/>(optional)"]
        HPA["HorizontalPodAutoscaler"]
        PDB["PodDisruptionBudget"]
        RB["RoleBinding"]
        CABundle["CA Bundle ConfigMap"]
    end

    KustomizePipeline -->|creates/updates| ManagedResources

    subgraph OGXServer["OGX Server Instance"]
        ServerPod["OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP"]
    end

    Deployment -->|runs| ServerPod
    Reconciler -->|health checks<br/>/v1/health, /v1/providers,<br/>/v1/version| ServerPod

    subgraph ConfigSources["Configuration Sources"]
        OperatorConfig["ogx-operator-config<br/>ConfigMap"]
        TrustedCA["odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>ConfigMap"]
        UserSecrets["User Secrets<br/>(ogx.io/watch: true)"]
        UserConfigMaps["User ConfigMaps<br/>(ogx.io/watch: true)"]
    end

    Reconciler -->|reads image overrides| OperatorConfig
    Reconciler -->|reads CA certs| TrustedCA
    Reconciler -->|reads API keys| UserSecrets
    Reconciler -->|watches config| UserConfigMaps

    K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"] -->|watch events| Reconciler
    Reconciler -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI

    style Reconciler fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style KustomizePipeline fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style LegacyAdoption fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style OGXServerCR fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style LegacyLLSD fill:#d0d0d0,color:#333
    style ServerPod fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,color:#333
    style OperatorConfig fill:#fff2cc,color:#333
    style TrustedCA fill:#fff2cc,color:#333
    style UserSecrets fill:#fff2cc,color:#333
    style UserConfigMaps fill:#fff2cc,color:#333
